ion if potential benefit is deemed to outweigh the risk.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/5856/', '', 'Dextropropoxyphene, Acetaminophen, Naltrexone', 'Lacosamide', 1767369485);
